'''2013年克羅埃西亞修憲公民投票'''是於2013年12月1日在[[克羅埃西亞|克羅埃西亞]]全國舉辦的[[公民投票|公民投票]]。本次投票決定了「是否將憲法制定的婚姻關係訂定為一男一女」的議題，也間接確認[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]的合法與否<ref name=BBC>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24873498 Croatia to hold referendum on same-sex marriage ban] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24873498 |date=20201201062537 }} [[BBC_News|BBC News]], 2013-11-08</ref>。最終投票結果為贊成者比例65.87%，高於反對者的33.51%而通過。此外，選民投票率約37.9%<ref name=Res01>{{citation|url=http://www.izbori.hr/2013Referendum/rezult/rezultati.html|title=State Election Commission of the Republic of Croatia, Preliminary unofficial results of the national referendum|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140120154152/http://www.izbori.hr/2013Referendum/rezult/rezultati.html|archivedate=2014-01-20|accessdate=2013-12-02}}</ref>。

此次投票最初於2013年5月時由保守教會背景團體{{lang|hr|U ime obitelji}}（In the Name of the Family）發起超過70萬人的連署公投<ref name=BBC/>，並獲得偏右政黨[[克羅埃西亞民主聯盟|克羅埃西亞民主聯盟]]（HDZ）和[[天主教會|天主教會]]的支持。[[克羅埃西亞總統|總統]][[伊沃·約西波維奇|伊沃·約西波維奇]]、[[克羅埃西亞總理|總理]][[佐蘭·米拉諾維奇|佐蘭·米拉諾維奇]]等執政聯盟方則持反對意見。

== 政治背景 ==
保守教會背景團體U ime obitelji已於2013年5月匯集超過70萬人的公投聯署。該提議是作為政府欲使同性婚姻合法化的因應。<ref name=yahoo>Lajla Veselica (1 December 2013) [http://news.yahoo.com/croatia-holds-anti-gay-marriage-referendum-041219323.html Croatia rejects gay marriage in referendum] {{Wayback|url=http://news.yahoo.com/croatia-holds-anti-gay-marriage-referendum-041219323.html |date=20131204124355 }} Yahoo. Retrieved 2 December 2013</ref>此公投案於2013年11月8日於[[克羅埃西亞議會|克羅埃西亞議會]]在151位議員中取得104票贊成而核准。<ref name=BBC/>

公投的問題為：「你贊成克羅埃西亞共和國的憲法修訂為婚姻是由一名女性與一名男性結合嗎？」

U ime obitelji宣稱為公民團體。但被懷疑有克羅埃西亞天主教教會以及如克羅埃西亞民主黨等激進的右翼政黨在背後指導。例如該團體的成員Željka Markić、Krešimir Planinić、Krešimir Miletić、Ladislav Ilčić，以及他們的家庭成員，同時都是克羅埃西亞民主黨的黨員。<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.24sata.hr/news/iza-u-ime-obitelji-skriva-se-stranka-jos-opasnijih-namjera-342459|title=Iza 'U ime obitelji' skriva se stranka još opasnijih namjera|trans_title=''In the Name of the Family'' is a public face of even more dangerous political party|accessdate=2013-12-05|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124182916/https://www.24sata.hr/news/iza-u-ime-obitelji-skriva-se-stranka-jos-opasnijih-namjera-342459|dead-url=no}}</ref>一個[[非政府組織|非政府組織]]團體Platform 112宣稱該公民團體的銀行帳戶為克羅埃西亞民主黨副主席Krešimir Miletić創辦之Građaniodlučuju、公民決定（The citizens decide）兩個協會所提供。<ref>{{citation |url=http://www.tportal.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/261911/Iza-inicijative-U-ime-obitelji-stoji-Hrast.html |title=Platforma 112: 'Iza inicijative 'U ime obitelji' stoji Hrast' |trans_title=Platform 112: HRAST is behind the initiative ''U ime obitelji'' |accessdate=2013-12-05 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220201659/http://www.tportal.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/261911/Iza-inicijative-U-ime-obitelji-stoji-Hrast.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

其中Željka Markić被反對者指稱為具有爭議的天主教主業會成員。她於2006年在[[薩格勒布|薩格勒布]]創立的主業會女性分支機構聘請一位西班牙公民Maria del Carmen Calvo del Valle。<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.tportal.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/301054/U-ime-obitelji-su-opasni-radikali-tipicni-za-Opus-Dei.html|title=BOGATI, OBRAZOVANI, ELITNI MRZITELJI DEMOKRACIJE - U ime obitelji su opasni radikali tipični za Opus Dei!|trans_title=Wealthy, educated elite haters of democracy - ''U ime obitelji'' are dangerous radicals typical of Opus Dei!|accessdate=2013-12-05|archive-date=2016-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161001043954/http://www.tportal.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/301054/U-ime-obitelji-su-opasni-radikali-tipicni-za-Opus-Dei.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，Željka Markić拒絕直接回答她是否為主業會成員。<ref>{{citation |url=http://www.slobodnadalmacija.hr/Hrvatska/tabid/66/articleType/ArticleView/articleId/213188/Default.aspx |title=Željka Markić odbila odgovoriti pripadali li Opusu Dei: Nije pristojno nekoga pitati koje je duhovnosti unutar Crkve |trans_title=Zeljka Markić refused to answer whether she is a member of Opus Dei: It is not polite to Church spirituality they belong to |accessdate=2013-12-05 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924122505/http://www.slobodnadalmacija.hr/Hrvatska/tabid/66/articleType/ArticleView/articleId/213188/Default.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 公眾意見 ==
一項於2013年6月舉行的[[民意調查|民意調查]]顯示55.3%的克羅埃西亞人支持這項議題，31.1%反對。<ref>[http://www.vecernji.hr/hrvatska/553-posto-hrvata-za-brak-zene-i-muskarca-u-ustavu-565686 55,3 posto Hrvata za brak žene i muškarca u Ustavu] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vecernji.hr/hrvatska/553-posto-hrvata-za-brak-zene-i-muskarca-u-ustavu-565686 |date=20160304051044 }} Vecernji, 6 June 2013</ref>

另一項於2013年11月進行的民意調查顯示54.3%的克羅埃西亞人會在這項公投投下贊成，33.6%反對，另有12.1%沒意見。政黨交叉分析方面，有85.7%的[[克羅埃西亞民主聯盟|克羅埃西亞民主聯盟]]支持者贊成，[[克羅埃西亞社會民主黨|克羅埃西亞社會民主黨]]則有39.5%的支持者贊成。<ref>[http://www.hrt.hr/index.php?id=vijesti-clanak&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=225168&cHash=006b964e4e Većina za proglašenje Vukovara mjestom posebnog pijeteta] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hrt.hr/index.php?id=vijesti-clanak&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=225168&cHash=006b964e4e |date=20190911223709 }} HRT, 2 November 2013</ref>

克羅埃西亞民主聯盟於投票前兩天發表的一項調查顯示59%的受訪者將投下贊成票，31%反對，10%沒意見。<ref>{{cite web| language =| publisher =克羅埃西亞民主聯盟| title =Na referendumu 59 posto građana za, 31 posto protiv| url =http://hrt.hr/index.php?id=vijesti-clanak&tx_ttnews[tt_news]=227831&tx_ttnews[backPid]=1070&cHash=23fe356410| author =| date =| accessdate =2013年12月5日}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

